title: The Money Pit
description: Walter and Anna want a home of their own. When Walter&#039;s real estate agent friend offers him what looks like the perfect home, Anna and Walter buy it. The house has many problems; structural, plumbing, electrical... These problems only come to light after they&#039;ve moved in. Hence, the house is a &#039;money pit&#039;. Also worthy of note are the comical builders and the terrible ex husband, Max, who still chases Anna.
